vernac_cmds: Theorem lcut : forall P Q R : L, P |-- R -> P |-- R -->> Q -> P |-- Q.
Theorem limplAdj_true : forall P Q, P |-- Q -> ltrue |-- P -->> Q.
Theorem landAdj_true : forall P Q, ltrue |-- P -->> Q -> P |-- Q.
Lemma lapply : forall P Q R, P |-- Q -->> R -> P |-- Q -> P |-- R.
Lemma lapply2 : forall P Q R S, P |-- Q -->> R -->> S -> P |-- Q -> P |-- R -> P |-- S.
intros; eapply lcut; eauto using lapply.
Lemma lapply3 : forall P Q R S T, P |-- Q -->> R -->> S -->> T -> P |-- Q -> P |-- R -> P |-- S -> P |-- T.
intros; eapply lcut; eauto using lapply2.
Lemma lapply4 : forall P Q R S T U, P |-- Q -->> R -->> S -->> T -->> U -> P |-- Q -> P |-- R -> P |-- S -> P |-- T -> P |-- U.
intros; eapply lcut; eauto using lapply3.
Lemma lapply5 : forall P Q R S T U V, P |-- Q -->> R -->> S -->> T -->> U -->> V -> P |-- Q -> P |-- R -> P |-- S -> P |-- T -> P |-- U -> P |-- V.
intros; eapply lcut; eauto using lapply4.
Lemma land_lor_distr_L : forall P Q R, P //\\ (Q \\// R) -|- (P //\\ Q) \\// (P //\\ R).
apply lorL; apply landR; try solve [ apply landL1 ; reflexivity ].
Lemma land_lor_distr_R : forall P Q R, (Q \\// R) //\\ P -|- (P //\\ Q) \\// (P //\\ R).
apply lorL; apply landR; try solve [ apply landL1 ; reflexivity ].
Local Ltac charge_search_prems found := match goal with | |- ?X |-- ?Y => solve [ found | apply landL1 ; charge_search_prems found | apply landL2 ; charge_search_prems found ] end.
Local Ltac charge_intro := first [ apply lforallR; intro | apply limplAdj_true | apply limplAdj ].
Local Ltac charge_intros := repeat match goal with | |- _ |-- _ -->> _ => charge_intro | |- _ |-- @lforall _ _ _ _ => charge_intro end.

Local Ltac charge_use := first [ eapply lapply; [ charge_assumption | ] | eapply lapply2; [ charge_assumption | | ] | eapply lapply3; [ charge_assumption | | | ] | eapply lapply4; [ charge_assumption | | | | ] | eapply lapply5; [ charge_assumption | | | | | ] ].

Local Ltac ends_with H ABC C := let rec go k ABC := match ABC with | C => k | _ -->> ?BC => let k' := (k; first [ apply landAdj_true in H | apply landAdj in H ]) in go k' BC end in go ltac:(idtac) ABC.
Local Ltac charge_apply H := match type of H with | _ |-- ?X => match goal with | |- _ |-- ?Y => ends_with H X Y ; etransitivity ; [ | eapply H ] end end.

Local Ltac charge_tauto := repeat charge_split ; solve [ charge_assumption | charge_trivial | charge_intro; repeat charge_intro; charge_tauto | charge_split; solve [ charge_tauto ] | match goal with | H : _ |-- _ |- _ => charge_apply H ; charge_tauto end | charge_use ; charge_tauto ].
Definition liff (A B : L) : L := (A -->> B) //\\ (B -->> A).
Local Notation "x <<-->> y" := (liff x y) (at level 78).
Lemma ltrue_liff : forall A B, |-- A <<-->> B <-> A -|- B.
Lemma land_cancel : forall A B C, A |-- B <<-->> C -> A //\\ B -|- A //\\ C.
Lemma uncurry : forall P Q R, (P //\\ Q -->> R) -|- (P -->> Q -->> R).
Lemma forget_prem : forall P Q, |-- P -> Q |-- P.
Lemma lrevert : forall P Q, |-- P -->> Q -> P |-- Q.
Lemma charge_and_use : forall P Q C, C |-- P -> C //\\ P |-- Q -> C |-- P //\\ Q.
Lemma land_limpl_specialize_ap : forall P Q L R G, L //\\ R |-- P -> L //\\ Q //\\ R |-- G -> L //\\ (P -->> Q) //\\ R |-- G.
Lemma land_limpl_specializeR_ap : forall P Q R G, R |-- P -> Q //\\ R |-- G -> (P -->> Q) //\\ R |-- G.
Lemma land_limpl_specializeL_ap : forall P Q R G, R |-- P -> Q //\\ R |-- G -> R //\\ (P -->> Q) |-- G.
Lemma landA_ap : forall P Q R G, (P //\\ Q) //\\ R |-- G -> P //\\ Q //\\ R |-- G.
Lemma land_lexists_ap : forall T (P : T -> L) Q R S, (forall x, S //\\ P x //\\ Q |-- R) -> S //\\ (lexists P) //\\ Q |-- R.
Lemma land_lexistsL_ap : forall T (P : T -> L) R S, (forall x, S //\\ P x |-- R) -> S //\\ (lexists P) |-- R.
Lemma land_lexistsR_ap : forall T (P : T -> L) R S, (forall x, P x //\\ S |-- R) -> lexists P //\\ S |-- R.
